Package: roboto-all-robopi1
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, roboto-base (>= 1.0.0), roboto-imu (>= 1.0.0), roboto-description (>= 1.0.0), roboto-motors (>= 1.0.0), roboto-example (>= 1.0.0), roboto-inference (>= 1.0.0), roboto-bms (>= 1.0.0)
Provides: roboto-all
Description: Metapackage for RoboParty robot software stack (robopi1 version)
 This package is tailored for standard RoboPi1 boards and installs all
 the necessary robot ROS 2 drivers, examples, models, and dependencies.

